\id PHM - Ekajuk New Testament 
\h Failimon 
\toc1 Failimon 
\toc2 Fai 
\mt2 NWER NYI POL NYONO TV 
\mt1 FAILIMON 
\c 1  
\nb  
\v 1 Me Pol ji li nne a ngbekobo tib go esi ji Kraist Jisos, a Timoti mmonanne ejahre, e kpꞌnyono nwer nyia tv Failimon ji kpo kor-r sꞌsehng, ye ji e kpꞌlimi eltum ano a ne.  
\v 2 Nwer nyia tob li ka Apia ji li mmonanne ejahre no nkal, a Arkipus ji tob li nne a nsoja ana wahr, a aneb ero ba kpo kono asi go ega etahk.\f + \fr 1:2 \ft Kol 4:17\f* 
\p  
\v 3 Nong, nnoobo jol a nahne, a elkoono ni lohng goji Esowo Nso ejahre, a Ntul a Jisos Kraist. 
\p  
\v 4 N kpo kak Esowo saam ngare anyehng anyehng nyi n lꞌbuum-a go egame ero bi n kpo kak,  
\v 5 tib eji n kpꞌwuku ana aneb Esowo kpee kpo kor-a,\f + \fr 1:5 \ft 1 Jon 4:20-21\f* fere wuk bade eltaame ni a kpꞌtaame tv Ntul a Jisos.  
\v 6 N kpo kak ero re, elkono ni ń kpo kono asi go eltaame ana ni a kpi no lub lim, wahn kahn elfuulu anehng anehng ni e kpi go ejang bi Kraist.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft Mak 11:24\f* 
\v 7 Mmonannee, wahr ebbel egburu eyebatahng, fere bel ekakeltim tib go ega elkoro. Tibre wo wo ma lim re eltim yebe abon Esowo. 
\p  
\v 8 Jol eji n kpi kpi esahb go ejang bi Kraist ji m bahk-a ma tong ji fuumu re wo lim,  
\v 9 n kp-a lub gboongo na tib esi ji elkoro,\f + \fr 1:9 \ft 1 Kor 9:12,15\f* me Pol ji li nnenkul, anv, m ma fere jol nne a ngbekobo tib go esi ji Kraist Jisos.  
\v 10 N kp-a gboongo ka Onesimus,\f + \fr 1:10 \ft Kol 4:9\f* mmon ewame, no me m ma jol nde\f + \fr 1:10 \ft 1 Kor 4:15\f*, eji n wob ngbekobo nyia.  
\v 11 Wuku wuku á jolo edemme nne ji a ki-e li nsehng anyehng anyehng, wo anv, yeblohko jol nne no bahk-a ma jo loko, fere tob jo lok-m. 
\p  
\v 12 Eji n kp-e tumu, á feere ba go ega, li ana n kpꞌtumu eltim ename tv-a.  
\v 13 Kor-m re á sa a name, eji á lꞌko nji nyi a jol-m loko ngare nyi n wob go ngbekobo tib go esi nnoobo etib.\f + \fr 1:13 \ft Fil 2:30\f* 
\v 14 N sebem re me n lim ejum ajehng ajehng njahm njahm, ki-a tohko lim, a kahn, eji a lꞌkꞌlim nnoobo enya ana bo bob-a na, a lꞌlim ana kor-a no go ega eltim.\f + \fr 1:14 \ft 2 Kor 9:7\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Fundiki ebfere jol re, Onesimus tahm-a sa mmongare ntiil, eji a lꞌfere bel-e go njinanjini.  
\v 16 Tibre anv, á kpeem li nju nyi nyi, yebfere jol nne no gbale sehnge nju. Yebjol akor-m mmonannee go ejang bi Kraist, no kpo sahb kor-m kor. Anv, á bahk-a koro elkohn ani, ye ji li nju enya, a mmonanne go ejang bi Ntul a Jisos?\f + \fr 1:16 \ft 1 Tim 6:2\f* 
\p  
\v 17 A lꞌbum-m ana nte ewa, lub ko Onesimus jang jang ana a jol-m koko.  
\v 18 Lꞌjol nyi á sood-a no, afi á fere bel-a mbong, nong, fere jol ana me n kpi-a mbong.  
\v 19 Me Pol, me wo kpꞌnyono ana go egame ebo re, Me wo bahke gale. Me m bum re, a kpꞌkahne re, a kpi-m mbong nyi elkpin ena ni wofono antahng.\f + \fr 1:19 \ft 1 Kor 4:15\f* 
\p  
\v 20 Mmonannee, n kpꞌsebe re me n li-a nsehng go ejang bi Jehova.\f + \fr 1:20 \ft 1 Tes 2:19\f* Lim, eji eltim ename lꞌjol yebe yebe go ejang bi Kraist.  
\v 21 N kpꞌnyono tv-a, tibre n kpꞌsahb kꞌkahn re, a bahke limi ana n tong-a no, jol sꞌsehnge na. 
\p  
\v 22 Fvfo, toobo ekpꞌkpa bum-m, tibre n kpꞌbumu re, Esowo bahke faange aro enyahne nya ń kpꞌkake, fere yak-m ka-n. 
\p  
\v 23 Epafras ji tob wob ngbekobo ana me tib go esi ji Kraist Jisos kp-a kake nnyo.\f + \fr 1:23 \ft Kol 1:7; 4:12\f* 
\v 24 Mak, Aristarkus, Demas, a Luk, bo ji e kpo lim eltum ano, bo kp-a tob kak nnyo.\f + \fr 1:24 \ft Kol 4:10,14\f* 
\p  
\v 25 Nong, nnoobo nyi Ntul a Jisos Kraist jol a nahne go egahne atohko.